#: ../../installation.rst:2 b0793ea8527140cab88897925110aa68
msgid "Installation"
msgstr "安装"

#: ../../installation.rst:4 45774995151741548129732108c0f582
msgid ""
"This page covers all supported installation methods for VoxCPM. If you "
"just want the fastest path to get started, see :doc:`./quickstart`."
msgstr "本页涵盖 VoxCPM 的所有受支持安装方式。如果你只想最快开始使用，请查看 :doc:`./quickstart`。"

#: ../../installation.rst:7 83d613f3f9344c56b2392dd716916d42
msgid "Requirements"
msgstr "环境要求"

#: ../../installation.rst:13 a3f128cf1114426bad5fcb21f1510961
msgid "Dependency"
msgstr "依赖项"

#: ../../installation.rst:14 2afebc78086e408285d666ae28539133
msgid "Description"
msgstr "说明"

#: ../../installation.rst:15 59462e9e84b147d88db2da7af8053c3b
msgid "PyTorch"
msgstr "PyTorch"

#: ../../installation.rst:16 e9a786b573844f54a566919a38eaf9ca
msgid "2.5.0 or higher"
msgstr "2.5.0 或更高"

#: ../../installation.rst:17 9afe31b9c6fa4a9cb5103ddad5e498f6
msgid "CUDA"
msgstr "CUDA"

#: ../../installation.rst:18 dce90393a6b04c76bdbaf4894082dea3
msgid "Optional. 12.0 or higher for NVIDIA GPU acceleration"
msgstr "可选。若使用 NVIDIA GPU 加速，建议 12.0 或更高版本"

#: ../../installation.rst:19 a8221731415b4f4781ece9be44d0af40
msgid "Python"
msgstr "Python"

#: ../../installation.rst:20 b3668f831a4b4232a5771b9f0dfb9521
msgid "3.10–3.12 recommended (3.10–3.11 most tested)"
msgstr "推荐 3.10–3.12（其中 3.10–3.11 测试最充分）"

#: ../../installation.rst:21 54a377e54c3143bcbf71a9d66bc2a33c
msgid "Disk Space"
msgstr "磁盘空间"

#: ../../installation.rst:22 b32f08d7382f466c93cc3f3faa11072e
msgid "Several GBs for model weights, depending on the checkpoint you use"
msgstr "模型权重需要数 GB 空间，具体取决于你使用的 checkpoint"

#: ../../installation.rst:26 4dcacfd0fd0d4f75adcf1b568fa72338
msgid ""
"CUDA is not required for CPU inference or Apple Silicon MPS usage. See "
":doc:`./faq` for Mac / MPS notes."
msgstr "如果你使用 CPU 推理或 Apple Silicon MPS，则不需要 CUDA。有关 Mac / MPS 的说明请参阅 :doc:`./faq`。"

#: ../../installation.rst:29 3647b7a36482495da439e5b4a3dcb115
msgid "Install with pip (recommended)"
msgstr "使用 pip 安装（推荐）"

#: ../../installation.rst:31 0acf0763f6924769adc7dc638de05014
msgid ""
"``pip`` is the default recommended way to install VoxCPM. It keeps setup "
"simple and matches the most common Python workflow."
msgstr "``pip`` 是安装 VoxCPM 的默认推荐方式。它配置简单，也更符合最常见的 Python 工作流。"

#: ../../installation.rst:33 ../../installation.rst:56
#: 85fe72fa03c94b7ebd9440693f19d221 86a64a49c94d42518910cb37d0a1be75
msgid "From PyPI:"
msgstr "从 PyPI 安装："

#: ../../installation.rst:39 7c4fabb35bed4a97b7ef100788dcadc3
msgid "From source:"
msgstr "从源码安装："

#: ../../installation.rst:49 3c3ad8825bb54f2e9aa17b8ee299f925
msgid ""
"Install with uv (secondary option)"
msgstr "使用 uv 安装（次选）"

#: ../../installation.rst:54 34626a4dcfb84029a568e62934119232
msgid ""
"`uv <https://docs.astral.sh/uv/>`_ is a good secondary option if you "
"prefer a managed environment and faster dependency resolution."
msgstr "`uv <https://docs.astral.sh/uv/>`_ 是一个不错的次选方案，适合偏好受管理环境和更快依赖解析的用户。"

#: ../../installation.rst:62 a8461976730e40bcb7a8a3dcd53bbfd9
msgid "From source (needed for running the web demo or local development):"
msgstr "从源码安装（运行 Web Demo 或本地开发时需要）："

#: ../../installation.rst:70 3c3ad8825bb54f2e9aa17b8ee299f925
msgid ""
"If you installed via ``uv sync``, run scripts with ``uv run`` to use the "
"managed environment. For example: ``uv run python app.py``, ``uv run "
"python scripts/train_voxcpm_finetune.py ...``."
msgstr "如果你通过 ``uv sync`` 安装，请使用 ``uv run`` 运行脚本，以确保使用受管理的环境。例如：``uv run python app.py``、``uv run python scripts/train_voxcpm_finetune.py ...``。"

#: ../../installation.rst:70 9bba325ddbae4ee6937e9f5d40f29ebc
msgid "The source installation is required if you want to:"
msgstr "如果你想进行以下操作，则需要从源码安装："

#: ../../installation.rst:72 5a6b9d4a6f804bb896f1a0dc32b934e7
msgid "run the local web demo (``python app.py``)"
msgstr "运行本地 Web Demo（``python app.py``）"

#: ../../installation.rst:73 0eb714b7d7064e0981360cfff3f5202b
msgid "modify VoxCPM source code"
msgstr "修改 VoxCPM 源代码"

#: ../../installation.rst:74 3ef1a20cdc1d499788407b05e1e44479
msgid "contribute to the project"
msgstr "参与项目贡献"

#: ../../installation.rst:77 0e7765dff61c490c9285b29a2accd673
msgid "Hugging Face mirror"
msgstr "Hugging Face 镜像"

#: ../../installation.rst:79 a8bb7ff9e3c74a3f80ee5a0c5c37a999
msgid ""
"If you have trouble accessing Hugging Face directly (common in some "
"regions), set the mirror before running any script:"
msgstr "如果你无法直接访问 Hugging Face（某些地区较常见），请在运行任何脚本前先设置镜像："

#: ../../installation.rst:85 1f28ce69c725461da6a0d8b48bdd3610
msgid "Model weights will then be downloaded through the mirror automatically."
msgstr "之后模型权重会自动通过镜像下载。"

#: ../../installation.rst:88 518ed29fa3aa449794627a4c0f2b8f03
msgid "Verify installation"
msgstr "验证安装"

#: ../../installation.rst:90 23a82b99a25048918dc112ea7b3228ea
msgid "After installing, run a quick check:"
msgstr "安装完成后，运行一个快速检查："

#: ../../installation.rst:96 abc94d145a1045b0b3e38100e9b0a1df
msgid "If this prints without errors, your installation is working."
msgstr "如果这条命令能够无报错输出，说明你的安装已正常工作。"

